---
name: Marketplace & Chat System
description: Service listings marketplace with deal-based chat, no commission model
type: feature
---
Revenue model: Subscription-first (no commission). Users list services for free as subscribers.
Featured Listings: Paid promotion via Stripe one-time payment.

Tables: service_listings, listing_inquiries, conversations, conversation_participants, messages
Profile extensions: bio, website, address, social_links, business_hours, certifications, gallery_urls, verified

Routes: /marketplace, /my-listings, /messages
Chat: Deal-based only (inquiry → conversation → messages). No random DMs. Realtime enabled.
Privacy: RLS ensures only participants see their conversations/messages.
